commit message:
Don't crash if the database has entries for items that no longer exist in the
schedule.

When loading a file online, write it to a temporary cache file before
overwriting a good cache copy with a possibly-bad one. (Saw someone getting
his cache overwritten with what was probably a hotel captive portal page.)

Unload schedules on phone timezone changes. this has to be done since most
schedule files are not timezone-aware and in-memory versions are.

Lower API version requirement. 1.5 is only 3.9% of the market at this point
but that's still >0 and apparently the app works perfectly on it.
